{"type":"message","id":"edf5d131","parentId":"896ed552","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:00:00.079Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:da4546e3-8bdd-4291-b88f-472a4b5d4b34 盘前选股+生成plan+上传] 执行每日盘前流程：\n1. 跑 myquant preopen 选股\n2. 读取选股结果 (top_y3.csv, top_y5.csv, market_regime.json, selected_industries.json)\n3. 用 Baostock 查每只候选股的前一日收盘价（adjustflag='2' 前复权），max_price = 前收盘价 × 1.02（2%溢价）\n4. 量化团队分析：决定买哪几只、各买几手、止损止盈比例、理由\n5. 生成 plan.json 并用 paramiko SCP 上传到云服务器 E:/Quant/strategies/plan.json\n6. 确认上传成功\n注意：\n- 账户用 68039812（模拟盘）\n- 资金限制 10万，单只不超过20%\n- max_price 必须从 Baostock 查前收盘价 × 1.02，禁止手动瞎设\n- Baostock 日期用 YYYY-MM-DD 格式，代码用 sh.XXXXXX / sz.XXXXXX 格式\n- SCP 用 paramiko，密码从 openclaw.json env.SSH_PASSWORD 读取\n- 代码格式严格按 plan.json 模板\n- 昨日涨停/接近涨跌停（±8%以上）的股票降低权重但不排除\n- Tushare 优先，Baostock 备选\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 08:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-02 00:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775088000078}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1488318","parentId":"edf5d131","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:00:44.961Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nI need to execute a daily pre-market stock selection process as defined by the cron task. Let me break down the steps:\n\n1. Run myquant preopen stock selection\n2. Read selection results (top_y3.csv, top_y5.csv, market_regime.json, selected_industries.json)\n3. Use Baostock to check previous day's closing prices for candidate stocks, calculate max_price = previous_close × 1.02\n4. Quantitative team analysis: decide which stocks to buy, quantity, stop loss/take profit ratios, reasoning\n5. Generate plan.json and upload to cloud server via paramiko SCP\n6. Confirm upload success\n\nKey constraints:\n- Account: 68039812 (simulation account)\n- Fund limit: 100,000 yuan, max 20% per stock\n- max_price must be calculated from Baostock previous close × 1.02\n- Baostock date format: YYYY-MM-DD, stock codes: sh.XXXXXX / sz.XXXXXX\n- Use paramiko for SCP, read SSH_PASSWORD from openclaw.json\n- Follow plan.json template format\n- Reduce weight but don't exclude stocks that were near limit up/down (±8%+)\n- Tushare first, Baostock backup\n\nLet me start by checking the current directory structure and existing files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<thinking>\nI need to execute a daily pre-market stock selection process. Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. First, I should check the current workspace structure and see what files exist\n2. Run the myquant preopen stock selection \n3. Read the results (top_y3.csv, top_y5.csv, market_regime.json, selected_industries.json)\n4. Use Baostock to get previous day closing prices for candidate stocks\n5. Calculate max_price = previous_close × 1.02\n6. Make trading decisions based on quantitative analysis\n7. Generate plan.json with proper format\n8. Upload to cloud server via paramiko SCP\n9. Confirm upload success\n\nLet me start by examining the current directory and existing files.\n</thinking>\n\n我来执行每日盘前选股流程。首先检查当前工作目录和现有文件结构。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4fc31c9fecba46d58ad48b68","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pwd && ls -la"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":38081,"output":479,"cacheRead":2874,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775088000079}}
